#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:232
msgid "Test distributed builds"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:234
msgid "Try building a new derivation on the *local machine*:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:236
msgid ""
"$ nix-build --max-jobs 0 -E \"$(cat << EOF\n"
"(import <nixpkgs> {}).writeText \"test\" \"$(date)\"\n"
"EOF\n"
")\"\n"
"this derivation will be built:\n"
"  /nix/store/9csjdxv6ir8ccnjl6ijs36izswjgchn0-test.drv\n"
"building '/nix/store/9csjdxv6ir8ccnjl6ijs36izswjgchn0-test.drv' on 'ssh://"
"remotebuilder'...\n"
"copying 0 paths...\n"
"copying 1 paths...\n"
"copying path '/nix/store/hvj5vyg4723nly1qh5a8daifbi1yisb3-test' from 'ssh://"
"remotebuilder'...\n"
"/nix/store/hvj5vyg4723nly1qh5a8daifbi1yisb3-test\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:250
msgid ""
"The resulting derivation changes on every invocation because it depends on "
"the current system time, and thus can never be in the local cache. The [`--"
"max-jobs 0` command line argument](https://nix.dev/manual/nix/2.23/command-"
"ref/conf-file#conf-max-jobs) forces Nix to build it on the remote builder."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:253
msgid ""
"The last output line contains the output path and indicates that build "
"distribution works as expected."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:255
msgid "Optimise the remote builder configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:257
msgid ""
"To maximise parallelism, enable automatic garbage collection, and prevent "
"Nix builds from consuming all memory, add the following lines to your "
"`remote-builder.nix` configuration module:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:259
msgid ""
" {\n"
"   users.users.remotebuild = {\n"
"     isNormalUser = true;\n"
"     createHome = false;\n"
"     group = \"remotebuild\";\n"
"\n"
"     openssh.authorizedKeys.keyFiles = [ ./remotebuild.pub ];\n"
"   };\n"
"\n"
"   users.groups.remotebuild = {};\n"
"\n"
"-  nix.settings.trusted-users = [ \"remotebuild\" ];\n"
"+  nix = {\n"
"+    nrBuildUsers = 64;\n"
"+    settings = {\n"
"+      trusted-users = [ \"remotebuild\" ];\n"
"+\n"
"+      min-free = 10 * 1024 * 1024;\n"
"+      max-free = 200 * 1024 * 1024;\n"
"\n"
"+      max-jobs = \"auto\";\n"
"+      cores = 0;\n"
"+    };\n"
"+  };\n"
"\n"
"+  systemd.services.nix-daemon.serviceConfig = {\n"
"+    MemoryAccounting = true;\n"
"+    MemoryMax = \"90%\";\n"
"+    OOMScoreAdjust = 500;\n"
"+  };\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

