#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/distributed-builds-setup.md:305
msgid ""
"Set the `nix.buildMachines.*.publicHostKey` field to each remote builder's "
"public host key to secure build distribution against man-in-the-middle "
"scenarios."
msgstr ""

